  dom_head_meta("description", "Self-Organized Criticality. Add grains to a sandpile. When any cell reaches 4 = K + sigma, it topples. Avalanches follow power laws. No tuning needed. SOC is THE method of the axiom: build the pile, criticality emerges.");
